text: Urangeline is a village community in the central part of the Riverina. It is situated by road, about 9 kilometres north from Urangeline East and 16 kilometres north east from Bidgeemia. Urangeline Post Office opened on 1 January 1882 and closed in 1934. ==Notes and references== Category:Towns in the Riverina Category:Towns in New South Wales Category:Lockhart Shire
title: Urangeline, New South Wales
